sequenceDiagram
    actor Customer as 客户
    participant UI as 前端 LoginView
    participant API as atm.js/http.js
    participant C as AuthController
    participant S as AuthServiceImpl
    participant DB as BankCardMapper/账户数据
    participant T as TokenManager
    Customer->>UI: 输入卡号和密码
    UI->>API: login({cardNo,password})
    API->>C: POST /api/atm/auth/login
    C->>S: login(LoginRequest)
    S->>DB: findByCardNo(cardNo)
    DB-->>S: BankCard
    S->>T: generateToken(cardNo)
    T-->>S: sessionId
    S-->>C: LoginResponse
    C-->>API: Result<LoginResponse>
    API-->>UI: sessionId
    UI-->>Customer: 进入主菜单

